name: Brainstorming Instagram Carousels
description:
Free to use Instagram Carousel template. It contains sizes for 1080xx1080px, 1080x1350px, Story 1080x1920.


And also containing two mockup templates for preview your post as also a story mockup template. It will automatically be updated.


On page Build Here you can duplicate the middle post how many times you want. It's Auto Layout based.


Updates - 26.11.2020

  • All components updated to AutoLayout 3


Updates - 17.05.2020

  • Added two more post templates with slice export
